            </div>
            <div className="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-green-100 rounded-xl border border-green-200 p-4 sm:p-6 shadow-sm">
              <h3 className="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-green-900 mb-3">✓ Store Status: Active</h3>
              <p className="text-xs sm:text-sm text-green-800">Your store is operating normally. All systems are operational.</p>
